                "PS"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A 1500-mu-m surface-barrier detector was",
                "used to acquire the data for angles > 20 degrees. In",
                "order to obtain better energy resolution, the data",
                "for angles < 20 degrees were obtained through the use",
                "of a 50-mm by 10-mm position-sensitive",
                "nuclear-triode detector, which was located in the",
                "focal plane of an Enge split-pole spectrograph."
              ]
            }
          ],
